dct_title_s: L'Afrique divisée en ses principaux etats
dct_description_sm: par le Sr. Janvier, geographe ; Scale approximately 1:32,000,000 ; Prime meridian: Ferro ; Relief shown pictorially ; Includes decorative title cartouche with flora and fauna ; Map numbered: '28.' ; Engraved by Jean Lattré ; Probably disbound from Janvier's Atlas moderne ; Paris : chez J. Lattré
